  subgraph MITIGATION["Why ML is a HINT — 7 Mitigation Layers"]
    direction TB
    M1["1. ML_WEIGHT_SCALE = 0.5
consensus can't CONFIRM w/o corroboration"]
    M2["2. Two-signal fast-path gate
ML OR Slither must flag"]
    M3["3. Per-class thresholds LOWER than 0.50
catch borderline cases"]
    M4["4. Prosecutor/Defender/Judge
LLM debate reads source weights ML as one signal"]
    M5["5. cross_validator prompt
explicitly names ML over-prediction"]
    M6["6. reflection (A.3)
flags known ML failure modes"]
    M7["7. explainer (A.8)
LIME attribution shows ml_pct vs others"]
  end

